---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import burningCharcoal from '../assets/burning_charcoal.png';
---

<section id="experiencia" class="experience">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="experience-content">
      <div class="experience-text reveal">
        <span class="subtitle">Poder y Calor</span>
        <h2>La <span class="accent">Experiencia</span> Black Root</h2>
        <p>Nuestro carbón no solo enciende, transforma. Con una combustión limpia y un calor constante y vigoroso, cada brasa es una promesa de perfección para tu parrilla. Siente el poder del fuego en su estado más puro.</p>
        
        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="number">100%</span>
            <span class="label">Natural</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="number">+2h</span>
            <span class="label">Calor constante</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="number">Min</span>
            <span class="label">Ceniza</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="experience-image reveal">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
          <Image src={burningCharcoal} alt="Carbón Black Root en llamas" width={800} />
          <div class="glow-overlay"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .experience {
    background: #050505;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .experience-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--accent-red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  
  .accent {
    color: var(--accent-tan);
  }
  
  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  
  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  
  .label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-tan);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  
  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  
  .image-wrapper img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  
  .image-wrapper:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .glow-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .experience-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    
    .experience-text {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    h2 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
    
    .stats {
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    p { font-size: 1rem; }
    .number { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
